@Aaron Vontell we always want to identify what we do support "a valid folder in the Instabase file system" (_now I'm looking to see if we define valid folders somewhere_)
I'll take a stab at adding "not the root directory of a mounted drive"

```You can now unzip a compressed file that has been uploaded to a valid folder in the Instabase file system. Unzip to the root directory of a mounted drive is not supported.```
